psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer

Class OrganismEnricherStatisticsWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.EnricherStatisticsWriter<Organism>
      • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.OrganismEnricherStatisticsWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, EnricherListener<Organism>, OrganismEnricherListener, AliasesChangeListener<Organism>, OrganismChangeListener

    public class OrganismEnricherStatisticsWriter
extends EnricherStatisticsWriter<Organism>
implements OrganismEnricherListener
    A statistics logger which records changes made by the enricher. Each addition, removal or update is counted and, upon the completion of the enrichment of the object, is logged in either a file of successes or failures depending on the enrichmentStatus.
    Since:
    18/07/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
